title: Gazprom to cut gas deliveries to Bulgaria and Poland | Ukraine latest

It is a non-aged, non-melting soft cheese made by curdling milk with a fruit- or vegetable-derived acid, such as lemon juice. Its acid-set form (curd) before pressing is called chhena. Paneer is the most common type of cheese used in traditional cuisines from the Indian subcontinent. title: Useful Kitchen Tricks To Feel Like A Super Chef
description: Prepare the kitchen tools because today we will become all-terrain chefs. We will be able to use any ingredient quickly and easily. Just pay close attention to these cooking hack and kitchen ideas that could save you in a pinch. We will have a fun time creating 5-star dishes for our family or sharing with our friends at a sleepover. So don't just stand there, go to your kitchen and let's start this class.||||Are you ready to learn useful kitchen tricks to feel like a super chef? Use a chopstick to create perfect crepes. We show you hacks to make the most of your sauces and jams. Discover an incredible tip to knead without getting your hands angry or making a mess in your kitchen. You can even create your own fruit and vegetable grater with an empty jam jar. title: Lembaga Survei Sebut Ganjar Pranowo Capres Terfavorit
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Pada periode survei Maret dan April 2022, 2 dari 3 lembaga survey mendapati Ganjar Pranowo sebagai capres terfavorit pilihan rata-rata 1.200 responden yang tersebar di 120 desa, kelurahan dari 34 provinsi.||||Seperti Charta Politika Indonesia, hasil surveI periode 10-17 April 2022 mendapati Ganjar Pranowo paling unggul dengan meraup 29,2% suara responden.||Menyusul prabowo subianto 23% dan Anies Baswedan 20,2%.Sementara 7 nama lainnya masih di bawah 5%. Responden yang mengaku tidak tahu atau tidak menjawab di angka 7%.||||Kemudian hasil survei Indikator Politik Indonesia juga menempatkan Ganjar Pranowo unggul telak dalam bursa capres 2024.||||Dalam hasil survei tatap muka periode 14-19 April 2022 Ganjar Pranowo unggul di atas Menteri Pertahanan Prabowo Subianto dan Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan.||||Elektabilitas Ganjar berada di angka 26,7%.||Selisih 2,8 % dari Prabowo Subianto atau meraup 23,9% suara responden.||lalu Anis Baswedan sebesar 19,4%.||||Selain itu, ada 10% responden yang tidak tahu atau tidak menjawab terkait capres favorit untuk Pilpres 2024.||||Pada periode 21-29 Maret 2022 hasil survei Populi Center menempatkan Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo dan Menteri Pertahanan Prabowo Subianto kompak berada dalam persentase elektabilitas tertinggi, yakni masing-masing 24%.||||Disusul Anis Baswedan, Sandiaga Uno, dan Ridwan Kamil. Masing-masing 12,1%; 6,3%; dan 5%. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283903/lembaga-survei-sebut-ganjar-pranowo-capres-terfavorit

title: Warstride Challenges - Early Access Gameplay Overview Trailer

Playable right now in early access on Steam, discover this intense and fun speedrunning game and learn how to shred demons into pieces in crazy trials with powerful abilities and weapons. |Gear up and race against the clock|Available on early access since April 19, Warstride Challengesâ€™ easy-to-learn but hard to master gameplay has already conquered a solid and growing community, and todayâ€™s video should now help newcomers take their first step, learn some tips and prepare to join the battle!|In this frenetic, fast-paced FPS, you need to race against the clock to get to the finish line. title: The New Mercedes-AMG C43 4MATIC (2023) Sound, Interior and Exterior Details
description: The latest generation of the Mercedesâ€‘AMG C 43 4MATIC sets new standards for innovative drive solutions both as a SaloonÂ and as an Estate. Following its premiere in the Mercedes-AMG SL 43, the AMG 2.0-litre 4-cylinder engine, the world's first series-production unit to feature an electric exhaust gas turbocharger, is now also being used in the C-Class. The new form of turbocharging guarantees particularly spontaneous response across the entire rev range and thus offers an even more dynamic driving experience. The turbocharger is operated via the 48-volt electrical system, which also feeds the belt-driven starter-generator (RSG). In the Mercedes-AMG C 43 4MATIC the unit produces 408 horsepower (300 kW) and, in certain driving situations, is able to call upon a brief additional boost of 14 hp (10 kW) from the RSG. The maximum torque of 500 Nm is available at 5000Â rpm.|The standard rear-axle steering, the AMG Performance 4MATIC permanent all-wheel drive with rear-biased torque distribution, the AMG SPEEDSHIFT MCT 9G transmission with wet start-off clutch and the AMG RIDE CONTROL suspension with Adaptive Damping System also contribute to the dynamic driving experience. In keeping with this, brand-specific features in the equipment and appointments as well as in the exterior and interior design emphasise the performance-oriented character of the new Mercedes-AMG C 43 4MATIC.|The C 43 4MATIC Saloon accelerates from a standstill to 100 km/h in just 4.6 seconds, while the C 43 Estate takes only slightly longer for the same exercise, at 4.7 seconds. The top speed is electronically limited at 250Â km/h in both models. title: Justin Bieber - I Feel Funny (Directed by Cole Bennett)
description: Lyrical Lemonade Presents|Justin Bieber - I Feel Funny|Directed by Cole Bennett|Now let me tell you the story of how this came about..|Justin randomly texted me this song one day and said "should we do a visual to this? song straight to number 1." We joked around about doing a video for it but never did. A few weeks later we were doing a pick up day for a video we had recently shot, but never finished (Honest).  We had a bit of time switching over from scene to scene. So, I went into his trailer and said "Remember that song you sent me? Let's shoot a video for it on my phone in between takes of the actual video." ... The rest was history. title: Tamil Nadu tragedy: Children among 11 electrocuted to dead in temple chariot procession
description: At least 11 people died from electrocution during a temple chariot procession in Tamil Nadu. Two among those killed were children and at least 15 others have been injured. The incident took place in the wee hours of Wednesday in Thanjavur district when the chariot came into contact with a high tension transmission line. Tamil Nadu CM Stalin has announced  â‚¹5 lakh each as financial assistance for the deceased. Those who had suffered injuries have been admitted to the Thanjavur Medical College. title: 'Do everything possible...': Angry China wants Pak to 'severely punish' Karachi blast perpetrators
description: A female suicide bomber killed three Chinese teachers and a Pakistani national in Karachi on Tuesday. This was the first major attack this year against nationals of long-time ally China working in Pakistan. The three were among passengers on a minibus returning to Karachi university after a lunch break when the bomb exploded at the entrance to the university's Confucius Institute. China in a strongly worded statement has condemned the attack and demanded Pakistan to severely punish culprits behind the Karachi attack. Watch this report for more.|#Pakistan #China #Karachi #Bombing #Blast #Baloch #Chinese

title: Sundar Pichai, CEO of Google and Alphabet
description: "You have to encourage innovation. Companies become more conservative  in decision making as you grow...be okay with failure and reward effort, not outcomes." |In this View From The Top interview, CEO of Google and Alphabet, Sundar Pichai, speaks to Archana Sohmshetty, MBA '22, about the impact of access to technology, humanity's challenge to harness it, and how Google is sustainably defining the future of work.  "When you see the appetite and the desire for people to make their lives better by gaining access to technology, that is what compels me to go beyond." says Pichai. #viewfromthetop

title: Polisi Disiram Air Keras saat Bubarkan Konvoi Motor Berkedok Sahur on The Road
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Anggota Perintis Presisi Polda Metro Jaya dilempar air keras saat mencoba membubarkan ratusan pemuda yang konvoi sepeda motor berkedok "sahur on the road" di kawasan Panglima Polim, Kebayoran Baru, Jakarta Selatan pada Rabu dini hari 27 April 2022.||||Rombongan konvoi ratusan pesepeda motor berkedok "sahur on the road" tersebut melawan tim dari Polda Metro Jaya dengan melemparkan air keras ke arah petugas saat dibubarkan.||||Baca Juga Panik Karena Akan Dibubarkan, Pebalap Liar Malah Tabrak Polisi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283748/panik-karena-akan-dibubarkan-pebalap-liar-malah-tabrak-polisi||||Beruntung petugas sempat menghindar dari lemparan air keras tersebut.||||Dari ratusan pemuda yang melakukan konvoi tersebut, sebanyak tujuh orang berhasil diamankan dengan barang bukti sisa air keras yang dimasukan ke dalam botol.||||Selain itu, petugas juga mengamankan rombongan balap liar yang sempat beraksi dengan membawa minuman keras.||||Polisi masih mendalami motif penyiraman air keras terhadap petugas tersebut.||||Baca Juga Tawuran di Akhir Bulan Ramadan Disebabkan Pelemparan Petasan dan Batu ke Rumah Warga pada Dini Hari di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283788/tawuran-di-akhir-bulan-ramadan-disebabkan-pelemparan-petasan-dan-batu-ke-rumah-warga-pada-dini-hari|||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283790/polisi-disiram-air-keras-saat-bubarkan-konvoi-motor-berkedok-sahur-on-the-road

title: Crowley vs Lopez HIGHLIGHTS: April 16, 2022 | PBC on Showtime PPV
description: (April 16, 2022) Canadaâ€™s Cody Crowley remained undefeated with a tough, punishing unanimous decision victory against veteran contender Josesito LÃ³pez in a 10-round contest of all-action welterweights that kicked off the PPV telecast. The scores were 98-91, 98-91, 99-90 for Crowley.| |Crowley (21-0, 9 KOs) sent Lopez to the canvas with a cuffing right hand that seemed to graze the back of Lopezâ€™s head and was deemed a knockdown by the referee. Though Lopez (38-9, 21 KOs) wasnâ€™t hurt in that sequence, he was wobbled throughout by heavy shots, his left eye nearly shut, and his legs unsteady in the later rounds.| |Still, as he has done against Canelo Alvarez, Marcos Maidana, Andre Berto and Victor Ortiz, the â€œRiverside Rockyâ€ soldiered on, refusing to let his corner stop the fight even though he was offering little resistance. Crowley, who, according to CompuBox landed 41% of his power punches and 53 of 440 jabs, was back in action following a sterling SHOWTIME debut in December 2021 when he topped previously unbeaten Kudratillo Abdukakhorov by unanimous decision. | |â€œI want to bring a world title back to Canada,â€ Crowley said. â€œCanada supports so much. title: Real gets ticket to Belgrade! | Playoffs Game 3, Highlights | Turkish Airlines EuroLeague
description: Real Madrid became the first team to punch its ticket to Belgrade when it completed a three-game sweep of Maccabi Playtika Tel Aviv with a 76-87 Game 3 road win on Tuesday and it will now seek a record 11th EuroLeague title.|ABOUT EUROLEAGUE BASKETBALL |Euroleague Basketball (EB) is a global leader in the sports and entertainment business, devoted to running the top European competitions of professional basketball clubs under a unique and innovative organizational model. Owned and administered by some of the most successful and historic clubs in the world, EB manages the continentâ€™s two premier menâ€™s basketball competitions, the Turkish Airlines EuroLeague and the 7DAYS EuroCup, as well as the sportâ€™s premier under-18 showcase, the EB Adidas Next Generation Tournament.|The EB competitions bring the elite of European basketball to all five continents and to the entire sports community through the OTT platform EuroLeague TV. EB also organizes a series of community and educational activities, led by the One Team program, in alignment with the United Nations Agenda 2030 Sustainable Development Goals. On the academic side, the EB Sports Business MBA trains future professionals in sports management.|About One Team|One Team, Euroleague Basketball's corporate social responsibility (CSR) program , supported by Turkish Airlines as the One Team Founding Patron and with the collaboration of Special Olympics as Proud Partner, uses basketball to achieve real social impact in our communities. With an innovative model of interconnectedness across an entire continent, Euroleague Basketball and its clubs have developed a complete CSR program that brings together activities from each team in an integrated, impactful way, working under the theme of "community integration" that actively addresses targets of the United Nations Sustainable Development Goal 10 on Reduced Inequalities. Each participating club develops a specific One Team project tailored to its own community needs to benefit groups in danger of exclusion due to problems such as substance abuse and gender, physical or intellectual disability. Since its founding in 2012, the One Team program has reached already directly and indirectly more than 23,000 participants through its various team projects.

title: The Juror that Didn't Listen

title: Tanks for Ukraine: How Germany's position has changed since the beginning of the war | DW News
description: The German government on Tuesday confirmed reports that it will approve a delivery of "Gepard" anti-aircraft tanks to Ukraine. German Defense Minister Christina Lambrecht announced the move during opening remarks at the Ramstein air base in Germany, coming at the start of a US-hosted defense conference on Ukraine.|Lambrecht also said that Berlin was working to train Ukrainian soldiers on German soil. "We are working together with our American friends in training Ukrainian troops on artillery systems on German soil," the minister said.|In recent weeks, Chancellor Olaf Scholz's government has come under increasing pressure for refusing to ship heavy weapons directly to Ukraine. Critics say his center-left Social Democrats (SPD) are too reluctant to stray from their historic policy of detente toward Moscow.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #tanks #Germany

title: Micic, Larkin push Efes to lead 2-1! | Playoffs Game 3, Highlights | Turkish Airlines EuroLeague
description: Anadolu Efes Istanbul finished the game on a 16-2 tear to defeat AX Armani Exchange Milan 77-65 in Game 3 of their best-of-five series to take a 2-1 lead. |ABOUT EUROLEAGUE BASKETBALL |Euroleague Basketball (EB) is a global leader in the sports and entertainment business, devoted to running the top European competitions of professional basketball clubs under a unique and innovative organizational model. Owned and administered by some of the most successful and historic clubs in the world, EB manages the continentâ€™s two premier menâ€™s basketball competitions, the Turkish Airlines EuroLeague and the 7DAYS EuroCup, as well as the sportâ€™s premier under-18 showcase, the EB Adidas Next Generation Tournament.|The EB competitions bring the elite of European basketball to all five continents and to the entire sports community through the OTT platform EuroLeague TV. EB also organizes a series of community and educational activities, led by the One Team program, in alignment with the United Nations Agenda 2030 Sustainable Development Goals. On the academic side, the EB Sports Business MBA trains future professionals in sports management.|About One Team|One Team, Euroleague Basketball's corporate social responsibility (CSR) program , supported by Turkish Airlines as the One Team Founding Patron and with the collaboration of Special Olympics as Proud Partner, uses basketball to achieve real social impact in our communities. With an innovative model of interconnectedness across an entire continent, Euroleague Basketball and its clubs have developed a complete CSR program that brings together activities from each team in an integrated, impactful way, working under the theme of "community integration" that actively addresses targets of the United Nations Sustainable Development Goal 10 on Reduced Inequalities. Each participating club develops a specific One Team project tailored to its own community needs to benefit groups in danger of exclusion due to problems such as substance abuse and gender, physical or intellectual disability. Since its founding in 2012, the One Team program has reached already directly and indirectly more than 23,000 participants through its various team projects.

title: Top US general: What's at stake is greater than Ukraine
description: General Mark Milley, chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff, discusses the stakes of the Russia-Ukraine conflict and the wider global implications with CNN's Jim Sciutto.  |Why Russia's Ukraine aggression matters to Americans|by Zachary B. Wolf|Nobody knows for sure exactly what Vladimir Putin is doing with around 100,000 Russian troops parked near the Russia-Ukraine border, but it's making the US and Europe extremely nervous.|President Joe Biden said this week he expected the Russians would "move in" and that a slight incursion would be met differently than a full-on invasion.|The US has spent the past few days cleaning up that remark and making clear any type of invasion is unacceptable.|Asked in Geneva by a reporter if he thought, like Biden, that an invasion was likely, Russian Foreign Minister Sergey Lavrov used some interesting language.|"Unless the United States doesn't go to bed with Ukraine, I don't think so," Lavrov said.|What does it mean for countries to 'go to bed'? All of this high-stakes geopolitical chess, then, comes down to how intimate the US gets with Ukraine in the eyes of Russia.|Read more at: https://www.cnn.com/2022/01/22/politics/russia-ukraine-us-what-matters/index.html|An important shift in Ukraine - and the US hopes more weapons will help|https://www.cnn.com/2022/04/20/politics/us-ukraine-weapons-what-matters/index.html|What does Putin want in Ukraine? title: Karachi Blast: Devastating moment when 'woman suicide bomber' pressed the button
description: A woman suicide bomber reportedly from Balochistan Liberation group killed four people, including three Chinese nationals, in an attack on a vehicle carrying staff from the Confucious Institute affiliated with the Karachi University. The CCTV footage of the incident shows a woman waiting for the van carrying Chinese nationals to come near her and then she detonated herself. Pakistan and China both have condemned the attack. Watch this video for more. |#China #Pakistan #Karachi #Terror #Bombing

title: Putin to UN chief: 'You've been misled' about Mariupol's situation
description: UN Secretary-General Antonio Guterres has held a face-to-face meeting in Moscow with Russia's president.||It is the first time the UN chief has visited Russia since the war in Ukraine began.||Guterres has offered direct UN assistance with the safe evacuation of the Azovstal plant in the besieged Ukrainian city of Mariupol where at least a thousand civilians remain trapped.||President Putin has called what's unfolding in Mariupol a difficult and tragic situation, and said he hoped talks with Ukraine would yield positive results.||||- Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/AJEnglish/||- Find us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/aljazeera/||- Check our website: https://www.aljazeera.com/||||#Russia #Ukraine #UN

title: Can I be myself at work? | Linden Vazey | TEDxUOA
description: In this TEDx talk, Linden talks about transitioning from a role in tech consulting to a career in leadership coaching, and one of the biggest challenges she face along the way which was answering the question â€œhow can I be successful at work and be true to my purpose?â€. After more than a decade in tech consulting for some of NZâ€™s largest firms, Linden hit a point that youâ€™re likely familiar with. She felt stuck in a story that no longer fit. Some part of her knew there was more to life than constant people-pleasing.|She didnâ€™t understand it at the time, but she was starting a journey of growth and realizing that much of her personality and ways of living were a defense. While it had kept her safe in the past, it was keeping her from growing into the wife, mother and leader she knew she could be. She decided that she wanted to really know herself, and to provide her children an example of a life led by courage, love and hope.|In 2020 she started â€˜Living on Purposeâ€™, where she helps professionals challenge their beliefs to create their own definition of success. This talk was given at a TEDx event using the TED conference format but independently organized by a local community. Learn more at https://www.ted.com/tedx

title: 5 Rolls Royces and a DUSTY Buick collection in the Appalachian Mountains | Barn Find Hunter - 114
description: Let's go back about six years when Tom met a gentleman named Howard at the Hershey Swap Meet. Howard told Tom all about his unique collection of GM barn finds, so they exchanged contacts in anticipation, one day, to film a Barn Find Hunter episode at his house. Well, that day has finally come! Howard has what could be considered one of the more unique Buick collections in the country, which consists of low-mileage and rare packaged mid-50s Specials, Supers, and Roadmasters. title: Waspada, ATM Anda Masih Bisa Terkena Skimming
description: Beberapa waktu lalu seorang nasabah Bank BCA mencuit di sosial media bahwa dana di rekeningnya mendadak hilang. Menurut pihak bank, nasabah tersebut diduga menjadi korban skimming. Bagaimana mungkin? Padahal saat ini hampir semua kartu ATM telah menggunakan chip. Koresponden CNN Indonesia Edo Ekarizky akan menunjukkan penyebabnya pada anda.

title: Kim Jong-Un's nuclear dare; Parades missiles, tanks, rocket launchers in Pyongyang
description: North Korea flexes military muscle to mark the anniversary of the countryâ€™s armed forces. title: 20 Best MCU Character Redesigns (And 7 Worst)
description: Thereâ€™s got to be some kind of superhero fashion industry rising to power in the MCU at this point. Throughout the ever expanding films of the Marvel Cinematic Universe, characters weâ€™ve come to know and love have gone through change after change. Others take a large departure from their comic counterparts and sometimes these look great, and others, wellâ€¦ When a character has been around for awhile, they just have to show up with some new threads time and time again. There are some characters on this list who have been through quite the roller coaster when it comes to their MCU design. From new capes, to shoes to haircuts and occasionally a full on color scheme change, letâ€™s take a look at the best and worst character redesigns in the MCU right now. |Sometimes, character changes can really affect the design of them in the MCU. Most of the time this really works well, and others not so much. From heroes to villains to Baskin Robbins workers, the character redesigns are sometimes top notch and sometimes a swing and a miss. Which character has gone through the greatest series of redesigns? Are they from Asgard or Sokovia? Be sure to leave a like and subscribe, and leave a comment with your answer. If you donâ€™t I have Kevin Feige on the phone right now and he is more than ready to give every single MCU character a Hawkeye Ronin mohawk. title: PDIP: Meskipun Jokowi Tinjau Sirkuit  Formula E, Interpelasi Tetap Jalan Terus
description: Presiden Joko Widodo meninjau sirkuit Formula E di Ancol ditemani Gubernur DKI  Jakarta Anies Baswedan. Jokowi dan Anies mengecek langsung kesiapan sirkuit Formula E yang rencananya akan digunakan pada 4 Juni mendatang. Kehadiran Jokowi di lintasan Formula E disinyalir sebagai restu atas gelaran ajang balapan mobil listrik tersebut. Apakah Fraksi PDI Perjuangan dan PSI tetap ngotot mengajukan interpelasi setelah Jokowi merestui Formula E?|Untuk membahasnya lebih dalam, simak pembahasan news anchor CNN Indonesia Rivana Pratiwi dengan Wakil Gubernur DKI Jakarta Ahmad Riza Patria dan Ketua Fraksi PDIP DPRD DKI Jakarta Gembong Warsono.

title: Is Europe trying to sway India away from Russia? | DW News
description: The European Union is desperate to boost ties with India and encourage New Delhi to reduce its links to Russia, its main arms supplier. Head of the European Commission Ursula von der Leyen on Monday called on India to align itself closer with the European Union as New Delhi attempts to balance its ties with Moscow and the West.  In a speech to the Raisina Dialogue, an annual conference held in Delhi, von der Leyen said a close relationship with the European Union was in the strategic interests of India. |She said India and the EU are "natural partners" who "thrive in a world of common rules and fair competition." But von der Leyen warned that these values were threatened by Russia and China. "The reality is that the core principles that underpin peace and security across the world are at stake," she said, going on to reference China and Russia's "no limits" partnership signed shortly before the invasion of Ukraine. She said the war was affecting not just Europe, but also the Indo-Pacific, already visible through the rising cost of food and fertilizer. The Commission chief said it was in the interests of the EU for the Indo-Pacific to remain open and become more prosperous. Therefore, she said, the EU was deepening its engagement with partners in the region, including ASEAN. Von der Leyen criticized China's "debt-trap diplomacy," which critics say allows Beijing to take control of ports and vital infrastructure. Instead, she advocated for the EU's Global Gateway program, which aims to invest â‚¬300 billion in partner countries. She said India could particularly benefit from this fund in the realm of climate change and energy production, and digital technology.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#India #EuropeanUnion

title: The ONE DRUG you need to reverse an Opioid Overdose
description: Employees of Hospitals, Schools, Universities and Libraries may download FREE medical animations from Nucleus by signing up for a free trial: http://nmal.nucleusmedicalmedia.com/free-trial-membership-a|#DrugOverdose  #OpioidAddiction #opioids|MEDICAL ANIMATION TRANSCRIPT: Opioids are drugs that are prescribed to treat moderately severe, or severe pain. Heroin, an illegal drug, is also an opioid. Opioid addiction is a brain disease where you have an overwhelming craving for the drug. You canâ€™t stop taking the drug, despite the harm it may cause you. An important treatment for opioid addiction is called medication-assisted treatment, or MAT. MAT is a whole-patient approach that combines medication to help you stop using opioids, with counseling and behavioral therapy. Three common medications used to treat opioid addiction are Methadone, Buprenorphine, and Naltrexone. In the brain, each drug attaches to the same receptors on cells as the addictive opioids. Methadone activates the receptors, but itâ€™s a slower acting drug than other opioids, because it takes longer to reach the brain when used as prescribed. This reduces the high feeling and prevents withdrawal symptoms. Buprenorphine is a weaker drug than addictive opioids, because it doesnâ€™t activate the receptors as strongly. It also blocks other opioids from attaching to the receptors. As a result, it reducing cravings for addictive opioids without making you feel high. Naltrexone blocks the opioid receptors by attaching to them, so addictive opioids canâ€™t. This prevents other opioids that get you high, from working. It does reduce cravings, but does not stop withdrawal symptoms. Drug treatment is more effective when combined with behavioral therapy. Therapy can help you handle stress and life events that can trigger cravings for opioids. Opioid overdose is a condition where taking too much of a drug may cause life-threatening conditions.Call 911 immediately if you think an overdose has happened. Start CPR if the person isnâ€™t breathing. The main treatment for an overdose is naloxone. Itâ€™s an injectable drug or nasal spray that quickly blocks the effects of opioids. You can help prevent opioid addiction and overdose, by taking non-opioid medication for pain when possible, taking opioids as prescribed by your healthcare provider, and doing physical therapy or exercising as recommended by your healthcare provider to help manage your pain. For more information about treating opioid addiction and overdose talk to your healthcare provider.|ANH21246

title: Henry Winkler Really Is the Kindest Man

title: One Of Britain's Biggest Unsolved Crimes: Who Killed Jill Dando? 23 Years On | This Morning
description: 23 years ago today, broadcaster Jill Dando arrived back at her London home and was shot on her doorstep. The murder, in broad daylight, of one of the nation's most loved television personalities shocked the entire county. To this day - just what happened that morning remains a mystery. The crime unsolved. Her killer never held to justice. It's a story we remember all too well, and one that investigative journalist Mark Williams-Thomas has followed for more than two decades. title: Pak vs Afghanistan fight escalates; Kabul drags Islamabad to UNSC over airstrikes
description: Kabul has taken Islamabad to UN Security Council for violating its territorial integrity by launching air strikes in Kunar and Khost province on April 16. A formal complaint against Pakistan has been filed by Naseer Ahmad Faiq of the previous Ashraf Ghani regime. He complained that the air strikes â€œis a flagrant breach of international laws, including humanitarian laws, the principles of UN Charter, the UNGA and UNSC resolutions, including resolution 1453 (2002) on Kabul Declaration of Good Neighbourly Relations.â€ Watch the video for more.|#Afghanistan #Pakistan #UNSC #UN #Khost #Kunar #PakAirStrikes #Taliban #AshrafGhani #UnitedNations

title: 'Can't make in China, sell in India': Gadkari to Elon Musk on Tesla vehicles
description: Union Transport Minister Nitin Gadkari has said that U.S. electric vehicle maker Tesla Inc is welcome to set up shop in India, make cars there for sale and export them, but must not import cars from China. He said that making in China and selling in India is not a good proposition. Tesla is desperate to import and sell its electric vehicles in India, having lobbied officials in New Delhi for nearly a year to cut tariffs, which the company's billionaire chief executive Elon Musk says are among the highest in the world.|#Tesla #ElonMusk #NitinGadkari #ElectricVehicles #EV #India #China

title: Elon Musk strikes deal to buy Twitter for $44bn - BBC News
description: The board of Twitter has agreed to a $44bn takeover offer from the billionaire Elon Musk.|Mr Musk, who made the shock bid less than two weeks ago, said Twitter had "tremendous potential" that he would unlock.|He also called for a series of changes from relaxing its content restrictions to eradicating fake accounts.|The firm initially rebuffed Mr Musk's bid, but it will now ask shareholders to vote to approve the deal.|Mr Musk is the world's richest person, according to Forbes magazine, with an estimated net worth of $273.6bn mostly due to his shareholding in electric vehicle maker Tesla which he runs. He also leads the aerospace firm SpaceX.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Twitter #BBCNews

title: A Strange Loop: Tiny Desk (Home) Concert
description: The Tiny Desk is working from home for the foreseeable future. Introducing NPR Music's Tiny Desk (home) concerts, bringing you performances from across the country and the world. It's the same spirit â€” stripped-down sets, an intimate setting â€” just a different space.|Josh Rogosin | April 26, 2022|Rather than use the stage at Feinstein's/54 Below, the cast of A Strange Loop cram into a booth for their Tiny Desk (home) concert. The protagonist of the musical is an usher, so performing in the crowd makes sense. 54 Below played a pivotal role in the musical's rise when, in 2016, composer Michael R. Jackson performed a concert version for New Musicals at 54. Little did anyone know that the show would go on to win the Pulitzer Prize for Drama in 2020. The cast reunited at "Broadway's Supper Club" to sing a five-song medley led by the show's author to celebrate their opening at the Lyceum Theater on Broadway.|Jackson explains A Strange Loop is "a musical about a young Black gay man named Usher who works as an usher at a Broadway show who is writing a musical about a young Black gay man named Usher who works as an usher at a Broadway show... who is caught in a self-referential loop of his own self hatred." The ensemble of characters joining him are a collection of "fierce but completely obnoxious" "Thoughts" â€” literally billed in the show's Playbill as "Thoughts 1-6."|The show at the Lyceum clocks in at 100 minutes with no intermission. Even in this small, Tiny Desk (home) version it's easy to get caught up in Usher's whirlwind of emotions as he's tormented by his thoughts. One can only imagine sitting in a dark theater with a bunch of strangers, laughing and crying, spiraling out together on Usher's strange loop.|SET LIST|"Intermission Song"|"We Wanna Know"|"Inner White Girl"|"Periodically"|"Memory Song"|MUSIC AND LYRICS|Michael R. Jackson|CAST|Antwayn Hopper|James Jackson, Jr.|L Morgan Lee|John-Michael Lyles|John-Andrew Morrison|Jaquel Spivey|Jason Veasey|BAND|Rona Siddiqui: music direction, keys|Beth Callen: guitar|Ian Jesse: bass|Marques Walls: drums|CREDITS|Video by Magicshak Media|Camera Operators: Nick Shakra, Anton Ponomarev, Maksim Kataev|Audio: Amanda Raymond|Audio Mix: Josh Rogosin|Directed by Stephen Brackett|Produced by Lilly Claar|Hair & Makeup by Kirk Cambridge Del-Pesche, Dotty Petersen, Elias Prince|Special Thanks: Raja Feather Kelly, Cherie B. Tay, Barbara Whitman, Jimmy Wilson, Arnulfo Maldonado, Corey Umlauf, 321 Theatrical Management, Feinstein's/54 Below|TINY DESK TEAM|Producer: Josh Rogosin|Video Producer: Michael Zamora|Audio Mastering: Josh Rogosin|Tiny Production Team: Bob Boilen, Bobby Carter, Kara Frame, Joshua Bryant, Maia Stern, Ashley Pointer|Executive Producer: Keith Jenkins|Senior VP, Programming: Anya Grundmann|#NPRMusic #TinyDesk #StrangeLoopBway

title: HIGHLIGHTS | Everton vs Arsenal (0-3) | Premier League | Foord, Mead, Nobbs
description: We secured another vital win in the race for the Barclays FA Womenâ€™s Super League title on Sunday with a dominant 3-0 victory over Everton. |It was a night of celebrations too, as Jordan Nobbs and Beth Mead reached 50 goals in the competition, with the latter also becoming the all-time top assist provider with 36 to her name. |We made a fast start at Walton Hall Park and Stina Blackstenius looked to have opened the scoring on the half hour mark with a fine finish, only for her goal to be incorrectly ruled out for offside. |We didnâ€™t allow that moment to kill our momentum, though, and with a stunning diagonal pass from Leah Williamson, Caitlin Foord was picked out inside the area and made no mistake in finding the bottom corner. |We continued to push on in search of a second before the break, but we were unable to provide the all-important finishing touch after creating two goalmouth scrambles. |Jonas Eidevall opted for a change after the restart with Mead shifting from right wing to centre forward, and his decision paid off almost instantly, with Vivianne Miedema teeing up our No 9 to fire home from close range for her 50th goal in the competition. |We werenâ€™t done there, though, as substitute Jordan Nobbs combined with Mead to score our third of the evening, playing a quick one-two before rifling the ball into the roof of the net. |#arsenal #arsenalwomen |Enjoy match highlights, training and behind the scenes to get closer to the likes of Bukayo Saka, Emile Smith Rowe, Vivianne Miedema, Nicolas Pepe, Alexandre Lacazette, Leah Williamson, Bernd Leno, Nikita Parris, Tobin Heath, Mana Iwabuchi, Jordan Nobbs, Takehiro Tomiyasu, Kim Little, Gabriel Martinelli, Aaron Ramsdale, Beth Mead, Ben White, Thomas Partey and more.|Subscribe to the title: Kaesang Tertawa di Postingan Bobby Soal Pria Ancam Patahkan Leher
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Putra Presiden Jokowi Kaesang Pangarep mengomentari kasus pria yang ancam patahkan leher Wali Kota Medan Bobby Nasution.||||Komentar Kaesang ini dilihat dari postingan Bobby yang menjelaskan terkait peristiwa pria ancam patahkan leher di akun Instagram Bobby.||||"Wkwkwkwkwkwkwkw," tulis Kaesang dalam kolom komentar IG Bobby.||||Menanggapi hal ini Bobby pun meminta Kaesang membalas WhatsAppnya.||||Baca Juga Bobby Nasution Sempat Dikira Preman oleh Pria Ancam Patahkan Lehernya di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283491/bobby-nasution-sempat-dikira-preman-oleh-pria-ancam-patahkan-lehernya||||"Mending kamu bales WA ku dari pada ngetawain," balas Bobby.||||Sebelumnya, diketahui pria bernama Rizkan Putra mengancam akan mematahkan leher Bobby Nasution.||||Rizkan ditangkap polisi bukan karena ancaman kepada Bobby. Namun karena melukai tangan petugas parkir yang ribut dengannya.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283550/kaesang-tertawa-di-postingan-bobby-soal-pria-ancam-patahkan-leher

title: Menteri Putin Sebut Zelensky Jago Akting Hingga Peringatkan Potensi Perang Dunia 3
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Menteri Luar Negeri Rusia Sergei Lavrov menyebut Presiden Ukraina Volodymyr Zelensky sebagai aktor yang jago berakting.||||Lavrov mengatakan hal itu karena Zelensky disebut punya kemampuan dapat meyakinkan negara-negara barat membantu Ukraina melawan Rusia.||||"Tentu saja dia (Zelensky) aktor hebat. Tapi jika Anda perhatikan lebih seksama dan membaca lebih awas apa yang dia katakan, Anda akan menemukan ribuan kontradiksi," tutur Lavrov dikutip dari The Moscow Times (25/4/2022).||||Baca Juga Keras! Zelensky Beri Pesan untuk Putin: Jika Melawan Ukraina, Anda Akan Kalah! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283480/keras-zelensky-beri-pesan-untuk-putin-jika-melawan-ukraina-anda-akan-kalah||||Menlu Rusia Lavrov juga mengingatkan bahwa kemungkinan perang dunia ketiga bisa terjadi.||||Ia pun meminta semua pihak tak meremehkan potensi perang dunia ketiga ini.||||"Bahayanya amat serius, hal itu nyata, Anda tak bisa meremehkannya"  ujarnya.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283552/menteri-putin-sebut-zelensky-jago-akting-hingga-peringatkan-potensi-perang-dunia-3

title: Best Shots from 2022 WGC Dell Technologies Match Play
description: The best shots of week at the 2022 WGC Dell Technologies Match Play.|â–º SUBSCRIBE: http://et.golf/Subscribe ||||The DP World Tour heads to Texas this week for the one World Golf Championship event of the season. The WGC - Dell Technologies Match Play will see 64 of the worldâ€™s best players compete in a round-robin format. Split into 16 groups of four, the player with the most points in each group will advance to single elimination play. Last yearâ€™s winner, Billy Horschel will be making a return to Austin Country Club, hoping to be the first player since Tiger Woods to win back to back match play titles. After gaining extensive match play experience during the 2021 Ryder Cup, Jon Rahm and Viktor Hovland will be in action alongside Bryson DeChambeau, Dustin Johnson and Justin Thomas. ||||Welcome to the Official YouTube channel of the European Tour. Every week you can find extended tournament highlights and individual player highlights from the likes of Rory McIlroy, Justin Rose and Tommy Fleetwood in events on the Race to Dubai. This is also the home of the 14 Club Challenge, Little Interviews, Fastest Hole and many more challenges, pranks and world record attempts featuring the biggest golfers in the world. ||||â–º WEBSITE: http://www.europeantour.com||â–º FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/TheEuropeanTour ||â–º TWITTER https://twitter.com/EuropeanTour ||â–º INSTAGRAM https://instagram.com/europeantour

title: Momen Rusia Gunakan Rudal Balistik Iskander Serang Ukraina
description: Kementerian Pertahanan Rusia merilis sebuah video peluncuran roket, melalui sistem Rudal Balistik Iskander pada Senin. Peluncuran ini dilakukan selama serangan militer di Ukraina.|Pihak Rusia menyebut mereka menggunakan senjata ini untuk menyerang depot senjata Ukraina. Serangan dilakukan setelah rusia mengonfirmasi data pengintaian.|Iskander adalah senjata presisi dengan jangkauan serangan hingga 500 kilometer. Sistem ini dapat menggunakan rudal balistik dan jelajah, yang menghasilkan gangguan elektronik tipuan di jalur penerbangan.|Iskander juga diklaim kebal terhadap pertahanan udara musuh. Senjata ini dapat terbang pada ketinggian yang sangat rendah, dan tetap tidak terlihat oleh musuh.

title: Bikin Merinding! Penangkapan Dramatis Perampok di Tol Pasirkoja Bandung
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Inilah detik-detik penangkapan dramatis dari pelaku perampokan di Tol Pasirkoja, Bandung.||||Video ini pun menjadi viral di media sosial. Terlihat sebuah mobil Honda Jazz dikepung polisi.||||Mobil tersebut berusaha kabur meski sudah dihalangi. Bahkan seorang polisi hendak ditabrak.||||Polisi pun harus mengeluarkan tembakan peringatan. Namun, tembakan peringatan ini juga diabaikan pelaku.||||Baca Juga Viral! Pria Ini Ancam Patahkan Leher Bobby Nasution Karena Enggan Membayar Secara Elektronik di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283371/viral-pria-ini-ancam-patahkan-leher-bobby-nasution-karena-enggan-membayar-secara-elektronik||||Dilansir dari Kompas.com (26/4/2022), Kabid Humas Polda Jabar Kombes Pol Ibrahim Tompo membenarkan peristiwa ini.||||Menurutnya peristiwa ini terjadi pada Senin, 25 April 2022 pukul 16.00 WIB.||||Pelaku merupakan pelaku pencurian dengan pemberatan Curat yang berjumlah tiga orang dan kerap melakukan aksinya di rest area.||||Dalam peristiwa ini pelaku pun akhirnya ditangkap polisi.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283548/bikin-merinding-penangkapan-dramatis-perampok-di-tol-pasirkoja-bandung

title: Momen Jokowi Gandeng 3 Kandidat Capres Terkuat: Prabowo, Ganjar, Anies!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Presiden Jokowi menggandeng 3 tokoh terpopuler yang digadang-gadang bakal maju Capres pada Pilpres 2024.||||Jokowi mengajak tiga bakal Capres yaitu Prabowo Subianto, Ganjar Pranowo dan Anies Baswedan pada bulan April 2022 ini untuk melakukan kunjungan kerja.||||Terbaru, pada 25 April 2022, Presiden Jokowi mengecek Sirkuit Formula E dengan didampingi oleh Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan.||||Baca Juga Pengamat Memaknai Ada Pesan Rekonsiliasi Saat Jokowi dan Anies Tinjau Sirkuit Formula E di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283457/pengamat-memaknai-ada-pesan-rekonsiliasi-saat-jokowi-dan-anies-tinjau-sirkuit-formula-e||||Saat kunjungan ini, Anies Baswedan tampak menyopiri Presiden Jokowi.||||Pada 20 April 2022 Presiden Jokowi melakukan kunjungan kerja dengan Menteri Pertahanan Prabowo Subianto di Madura.||||Presiden Jokowi dan Prabowo kompak membeli blankon merah.||||Lalu pada 13 April 2022 lalu, Presiden Jokowi menggandeng Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo saat melakukan kunjungan kerja di wilayah Jawa Tengah.||||Baca Juga Ganjar Setuju Kebijakan Terbaru Jokowi soal Minyak Goreng: Seribu Persen Benar, Harus Didukung di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282999/ganjar-setuju-kebijakan-terbaru-jokowi-soal-minyak-goreng-seribu-persen-benar-harus-didukung||||Ganjar Pranowo pun mendampingi Jokowi melakukan kunjungan kerja di Pasar Brebes.||||Jika dilihat dari Survei Litbang Kompas, 3 tokoh tersebut mempunyai elektabilitas teratas menjadi kandidat Calon Presiden untuk Pilpres 2024 mendatang.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283496/momen-jokowi-gandeng-3-kandidat-capres-terkuat-prabowo-ganjar-anies

title: KETUM PSSI MOCHAMAD IRIAWAN TEMUI RAMAI RUMAKIEK DI JAKARTA | PSSI CORNER
description: Ketua Umum PSSI, Mochamad Iriawan memberikan perhatian khusus kepada pemain sayap Timnas Indonesia, Ramai Rumakiek. Hal ini setelah pemain asal Papua tersebut mengalami cedera otot.|Rumakiek pun didatangkan dari Jayapura, Papua pada Senin (25/4) untuk menjalani pengobatan hingga sembuh. Untuk itu, Ketum PSSI memberikan perintah kepada Head of Medis PSSI, Dokter Syarif Alwi untuk menangani hal ini.|Pada Selasa (26/4) ini, Rumakiek akan menjalani pengobatan di Rumah Sakit Royal Progress, Jakarta. Ia diharapkan tidak butuh waktu lama untuk sembuh dan segera bergabung bersama Garuda Muda.|Seperti diketahui, Tim U-23 Indonesia sedang mengikuti pemusatan latihan (TC) di Korea Selatan untuk mengikuti SEA Games 2021 mendatang.|Indonesia tergabung di grup A bersama tuan rumah Vietnam, Filipina, Timor Leste, dan Myanmar. Rahmat Irianto dan kawan-kawan akan menghadapi laga pertama pada tanggal 6 Mei mendatang melawan tuan rumah Vietnam.|#timnasindonesia #pssi

title: Mysterious Hepatitis Outbreak Among Children
description: Health experts are warning of a mysterious hepatitis outbreak in children. Though most infections are in the U.K., there are now three suspected cases in Illinois. Two cases have been reported in North Carolina and nine in Alabama. According to health officials, at least one child died from the outbreak. NBC Newsâ€™ Dr. John Torres says that the concern comes from not knowing the outbreakâ€™s source. As passionate fans of these shows, we provide news, analysis and fan engagement on Americaâ€™s Got Talent, Britainâ€™s Got Talent, The Masked Singer, The Voice, The X Factor, American Idol, The Four and its contestants.|ABOUT AMERICAN IDOL|AMERICAN IDOL, the iconic series that revolutionized the television landscape by pioneering the music competition genre, returned to the airwaves in February 2021 for its forth season at its new home on ABC. The nationwide search for the next superstar kicked off in August 2019, as the virtual Idol Bus traveled from Portland, Oregon, to Orlando, Florida, in its pursuit for talent, covering many cities across the country. title: Bulldozers to roll in Shaheen Bagh after Jahangirpuri? SDMC to launch 'anti-encroachment' drive
description: South Delhi Municipal Corporation (SDMC) has prepared a plan to carry out the anti-encroachment drive in its jurisdiction. The SDMC mayor Mukesh Suryan said the civic body will soon take action against alleged encroachers. The BJP-controlled SDMC said that an action plan to remove alleged encroachment has been readied. The civic body claimed that Rohingyas and Bangladeshis have encroached state land in various areas. The civic body further claimed that illegal activities are taking place on the encroached govt land. Watch the full video for more.|#Delhi #ShaheenBagh #Jahangirpuri #SDMC #DelhiCivicbody

title: Johnny Depp Questions Why He's 'Guilty Until Proven Innocent' During Testimony
description: Johnny Depp recalls how he felt when he received the news he would no longer be a part of the 'Pirates of the Caribbean' franchise. During his ongoing defamation trial against Amber Heard, the actor shares that he hoped the Disney films would have had a chance to have a proper goodbye for his character, Captain Jack Sparrow. Depp also includes that if it were his choice, he would have stayed until the end.

title: EU red flags to India 'no limits' Russia-China friendship; Warns of Ukraine impact in Indo-Pacific

title: Keras! Zelensky Beri Pesan untuk Putin: Jika Melawan Ukraina, Anda Akan Kalah!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Presiden Ukraina Volodymyr Zelensky bersikeras menyatakan bahwa negaranya tak akan kalah dari Rusia.||||Zelensky beri pesan untuk presiden Rusia Vladimir Putin bahwa Rusia tak akan menang dalam peperangan yang tengah berlangsung ini.||||"Jika Anda akan menghancurkan tetangga, Anda akan kalah. Jika Anda ingin memulihkan kerajaan lama, Anda akan kalah," ujar Zelensky dalam sebuah video.||||Baca Juga Putin Murka, Tuding Barat Lancarkan Teror untuk Hancurkan Rusia dari Dalam di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283363/putin-murka-tuding-barat-lancarkan-teror-untuk-hancurkan-rusia-dari-dalam||||"Dan jika Anda melawan Ukraina, Anda akan kalah," lanjutnya.||||Zelensky menyebut bahwa seluruh warga Ukraina terus mendambakan berhentinya perang dan datangnya kedamaian.||||Ia pun mengatakan bahwa kehadiran militer Rusia di Ukraina tak akan lama, dan membuat mereka tak tahan berada di Ukraina.||||"Ketika kemenangan datang, semua orang akan merasakannya, ketika kedamaian datang, semua orang akan melihatnya," ucap Zelensky.||||"Tetapi untuk mewujudkannya lebih cepat, kita tidak harus memikirkan kapan dan apa yang akan terjadi. Kita harus berpikir setiap hari tentang bagaimana membuat kehadiran penjajah di tanah kita semakin tak tertahankan."||||Video Editor: Febi Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283480/keras-zelensky-beri-pesan-untuk-putin-jika-melawan-ukraina-anda-akan-kalah

title: Houseplants for Different Areas | Ask This Old House
description: In this video, This Old House landscape expert Jenn Nawada takes us to a local greenhouse to discuss how to choose houseplants for any room.|SUBSCRIBE to This Old House: http://bit.ly/SubscribeThisOldHouse.|Landscape contractor Jenn Nawada meets a plant expert at a local greenhouse to talk about different houseplants and tropical plants. The two discuss the importance of the direction windows face, as it determines how much sunlight the room will get. Matching this sunlight to the right type of plants will allow them to thrive.|Looking for more step by step guidance on how to complete projects around the house? Join This Old House Insider to stream over 1,000 episodes commercial-free: https://bit.ly/2GPiYbH|Plus, download our FREE app for full-episode streaming to your connected TV, phone or tablet:  https://www.thisoldhouse.com/pages/streaming-app|Room and Window Layout Come First|Before deciding on which plants youâ€™d like for a particular room, itâ€™s important to consider the room and window layout. Different plant species thrive in different light conditions, and the direction the window faces determines the amount of light.|In the northern hemisphere, windows on the south side of a home will get full sunlight. Windows on the east or west are considered partial sunlight. Windows on the north side of the home are considered full shade.|Keep in mind that these are general rules. Structures like tall buildings, trees, and other obstructions can greatly reduce the amount of sunlight a window gets.|Shaded Windows|Plants in shaded windows need to thrive in low light conditions. Floor plants like bamboo palms can fill up a shaded corner, while a Chinese evergreen will bring interest as a table plant. For hanging plants, look for different varieties of pothos.|Partial Light|Windows on the east and west side of a home, or south-facing windows semi-obstructed by buildings or trees, will receive partial light. Floor plants that thrive in these conditions are Dracaena or dragon trees, as do tabletop plants like birds nest ferns. When it comes to hanging baskets or trailing plants, consider Swiss cheese vines.|Full Sun|South-facing windows are the most likely to see a lot of sunlight, and the plants in these windows need to be capable of handling it. Crotons do well as floor plants in these windows, and snake plants are a great choice for tabletop interest (theyâ€™re incredibly hardy, as well). String succulents like String of Pearls, String of Bananas, String of Hearts, or String of Dolphins plants can also thrive in these bright, intense windows.|Where to find it?|Jenn Nawada and Chris Bell, the houseplants and tropical plants expert at Weston Nurseries [https://www.westonnurseries.com/locations/hopkinton-garden-center/], gives insight on how to choose houseplants for different areas of a home.|About Ask This Old House TV:|From the makers of This Old House, Americaâ€™s first and most trusted home improvement show, Ask This Old House answers the steady stream of home improvement questions asked by viewers across the United States. Covering topics from landscaping to electrical to HVAC and plumbing to painting and more. Ask This Old House features the experts from This Old House, including general contractor Tom Silva, plumbing and heating expert Richard Trethewey, landscape contractor Jenn Nawada, master carpenter Norm Abram, and host Kevin Oâ€™Connor. ASK This Old House helps you protect and preserve your greatest investmentâ€”your home.|Follow This Old House:|Facebook: http://bit.ly/ThisOldHouseFB|Twitter: http://bit.ly/ThisOldHouseTwitter|Pinterest: http://bit.ly/ThisOldHousePinterest|Instagram: http://bit.ly/ThisOldHouseIG|Houseplants for Different Areas | Ask This Old House|https://www.youtube.com/user/thisoldhouse/

title: Toddler Goes Viral For Adorable Interaction With Impromptu NYC Photoshoot
description: It's amazing how kids can be so mesmerized by things that seem relatively simple to grownups. Los Angeles illustrator Monica Ahanonu was visiting New York City for a gala, and caught the attention of a little girl while taking photos on the street. Pilot Pen awards Monica $1,000 for her sweet interaction. title: Netflix Cancels Multiple Shows After Subscriber Drop - IGN The Fix: Entertainment
description: Following Netflix's highly publicized subscriber loss, Netflix is now canceling certain animated shows, putting a pause on development, and firing executives. Along with getting rid of its Director of Creative Leadership and Development for Original Animation and his staff, Netflix canceled the highly anticipated animated adaptation of the Bone comic series. Based on the comic by Jeff Smith, the Bone series was announced back in 2019. But that wasn't the only animated show to get the proverbial bone from #Netflix - the animated adaptation of Roald Dahl's The Twits, and Lauren Faust's Toil and Trouble were also canceled, though the former will reportedly live on as a feature film. While Netflix is cutting back on animation, it's reportedly spending $30 million dollars per episode on Stranger Things season 4. And the director of The Mummy movie, starring Tom Cruise, says the failed film made him a better director.|#IGN #DailyFix

title: Xbox Hiring to Help It Find More Acquisitions - IGN Daily Fix
description: Today on IGN The Fix: Games,   Xbox is hiring a new employee to help manage its merger and acquisitions programme - suggesting that there may well be more studio acquisitions in its future. As reported by Video Games Chronicle, Microsoft is seeking a Manager of Gaming Strategy and Development whose responsibilities will include, "Developing and evaluating the business case for content & technology acquisitions." It seems to indicate the company has no plans to slow down its purchasing of developers and other gaming companies.  Game developers are upset over an Apple policy change that will see apps deleted if they've not been recently updated. On Twitter, Protopop Games (below) shared an email from Apple that said their app had not been updated in "a significant amount of time" and would therefore be deleted from the App Store.  Diablo: Immortal is now coming to PC as well as mobile - and it will arrive for both platforms on June 2. The MMO was originally announced solely for Android and iOS, but Blizzard Entertainment revealed in a blog post that a PC port will be released in open beta alongside the mobile version.|#IGN #DailyFix

title: Twitter accepts Elon Musk's $44 billion takeover bid | DW News
description: The board of Twitter approved Elon Musk's takeover bid. The deal is expected to close this year. The price is a 38% premium on Twitter's closing price on April 1, just before Musk announced a 9% stake in the company.|The chief executive of SpaceX and Tesla took a major stake in the social media firm earlier this month before making a formal purchase offer. Musk said he had lined up about $46.5 billion (â‚¬43.4 billion) in financing.|"Free speech is the bedrock of a functioning democracy, and Twitter is the digital town square where matters vital to the future of humanity are debated," the world's richest man said in a joint statement with Twitter. title: Ree Drummond's Tex-Mex Chicken Pot Pie | The Pioneer Woman | Food Network
description: Ree mixes three kinds of chile peppers with fresh corn and shredded chicken for this spiced up take on a comfort food classic!|Watch #ThePioneerWoman, Saturdays at 10a|9c + subscribe to #discoveryplus to stream the entire library and so much more: http://discoverypl.us/2NeKVgd. |Get the recipe â–¶ https://foodtv.com/3jV6G1G|Subscribe to Food Network â–¶ http://foodtv.com/YouTube|Take one sassy former city girl, her hunky rancher husband, a band of adorable kids, an extended family, cowboys, 3,000 wild mustangs, a herd of cattle and one placid basset hound and you have The Pioneer Woman. The Pioneer Woman is an open invitation into Ree Drummond's life: The award-winning blogger and best-selling cookbook author comes to Food Network and shares her special brand of home cooking, from throw-together suppers to elegant celebrations. The series, set against the incredible story of life at home on the range, is the next best thing to actually sitting on a stool in Ree's kitchen.|Welcome to Food Network, where learning to cook is as simple as clicking play! Grab your apron and get ready to get cookin' with some of the best chefs around the world. We'll give you a behind-the-scenes look at our best shows, take you inside our favorite restaurant and be your resource in the kitchen to make sure every meal is a 10/10!|Tex-Mex Chicken Pot Pie|RECIPE COURTESY OF REE DRUMMOND|Level: Intermediate|Total: 2 hr 5 min (includes chilling and cooling time)|Active: 1 hr 5 min|Yield: 4 to 6 servings|Ingredients|4 tablespoons salted butter|2 jalapeÃ±o peppers, stemmed, seeded and diced |2 poblano peppers, stemmed, seeded and diced |2 corncobs, kernels removed |1 large yellow onion, diced |Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper |1/4 cup all-purpose flour, plus more for dusting |2 cups chicken broth |1 cup heavy cream |1/4 cup chopped fresh cilantro |2 canned chipotle peppers, chopped |3 cups shredded rotisserie chicken |1/2 recipe Perfect Pie Crust, recipe follows, or your favorite pie crust|All-purpose flour, for dusting|1 large egg, beaten |1/2 cup grated pepper jack cheese |Perfect Pie Crust:|3 cups all-purpose flour|1 teaspoon kosher salt |3/4 cup (1 1/2 sticks) salted butter, cut into small pieces |3/4 cup vegetable shortening, cut into small pieces |1 large egg |1 tablespoon distilled white vinegar |5 tablespoons cold water, or more as needed |Directions|Preheat the oven to 400 degrees F.|Melt the butter in a 10-inch skillet over medium heat. Add the jalapeÃ±o and poblano peppers, corn and onion. Season with a pinch of salt and pepper. Cook to soften the vegetables, 2 to 3 minutes.|Sprinkle the flour over the vegetables and stir until the flour has coated the vegetables, a minute or two (avoid letting the flour stick to the bottom of the skillet). Stirring constantly, slowly add the chicken broth. Stir in the cream, cilantro and chipotle peppers. Allow the sauce to come to the boil and thicken, 2 to 3 minutes. Remove from the heat, then taste and adjust the seasoning. Add the chicken and stir to combine.|Roll out the Pie Crust on a lightly-floured surface to an 11-inch circle, large enough to hang over the skillet. Carefully lay the crust over the skillet, pressing gently into the sides to seal. Brush the top with the beaten egg and sprinkle over the pepper jack cheese. Cut 2 to 3 small slits in the top and bake until the crust is golden, about 30 minutes. Cool slightly before serving, 10 minutes or so.|Perfect Pie Crust:|Yield: 2 pie crusts|Combine the flour, salt, butter and shortening in a large bowl.|Using a pastry cutter, gradually work it all together until the mixture resembles coarse crumbs.|Beat the egg with a fork and add it to the mixture along with the vinegar.|Add the cold water.|Stir it all together until it comes together, adding another tablespoon or two of water if it needs the moisture.|Form the mixture into 2 balls and wrap them in individual plastic bags. If using immediately, chill for 20 minutes in the refrigerator before rolling out. If freezing, remove them from the freezer 30 minutes before you are ready to use them.|Subscribe to our channel to fill up on the latest must-eat recipes, brilliant kitchen hacks and content from your favorite Food Network shows.|â–¶ FOOD NETWORK KITCHEN APP: http://foodtv.com/FNKApp|â–¶ WEBSITE: https://www.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FULL EPISODES: https://watch.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ TWITTER: https://twitter.com/FoodNetwork|#ReeDrummond #ThePioneerWoman #FoodNetwork #TexMexChickenPotPie|Ree Drummond's Tex-Mex Chicken Pot Pie | The Pioneer Woman | Food Network|https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-HrzsvpDi54

title: BMKG Rilis Kondisi Gunung Anak Krakatau Naik ke Level III, Siaga!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Badan Meteorologi Klimatologi dan Geofisika (BMKG), pada Senin (25/04) malam merilis Kondisi Gunung Anak Krakatau yang kembali mengalami erupsi dengan status naik dari waspada atau level dua menjadi siaga atau level tiga.||||Erupsi Gunung Anak Krakatau terjadi karena ada peningkatan aktivitas Gunung Anak Krakatau pada bulan April ini.||||Baca Juga Aktivitas Anak Krakatau Meningkat, BMKG Imbau Siap Siaga, Waspada Potensi Tsunami pada Malam Hari di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283372/aktivitas-anak-krakatau-meningkat-bmkg-imbau-siap-siaga-waspada-potensi-tsunami-pada-malam-hari||||Karena pernah menimbulkan tsunami maka bmkg mengimbau agar masyarakat waspada terhadap potensi gelombang tinggi atau tsunami terutama di malam hari.||||Pusat Vulkanologi dan Mitigasi Bencana Geologi (PVMBG) mengumumkan status aktivitas Gunung Anak Krakatau (GAK) naik ke tingkat Level 3 Siaga, dan potensi bahaya serta rekomendasi yang harus diwaspadai.||||"Hasil pemantauan visual dan instrumental menunjukkan adanya kenaikan aktivitas yang semakin signifikan di Gunung Anak Krakatau dinaikkan dari Waspada (Level II) menjadi Siaga (Level III) terhitung sejak tanggal 24 April 2022, pukul 18.00 WIB," dikutip Kompas.com dalam laman resmi Badan Geologi Kementerian Energi dan Sumber Daya Mineral (ESDM), Senin (25/4/2022).||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283436/bmkg-rilis-kondisi-gunung-anak-krakatau-naik-ke-level-iii-siaga

title: War in Ukraine: Zelenskyy calls on West to supply heavy weapons | DW News
description: The US promised Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy hundreds of millions of dollars in new aid. The announcement came after US Secretary of State Antony Blinken and Defense Secretary Lloyd Austin met Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy in Kyiv on Sunday.|Russia's Foreign Ministry says it has declared 40 employees of German diplomatic institutions in Russia "persona non grata." In a statement, the ministry said it had summoned Germany's ambassador in Moscow and handed him a note. The ministry said it was "a symmetrical response" to the German government's decision to expel 40 Russian diplomats from Germany on April 4.|Estonian Prime Minister Kaja Kallas has told DW that her country expects Germany to show strong leadership and deter Russian aggression. The comments come with the German government facing criticism over its reluctance to ban Russian oil and send heavy weapons such as tanks to Ukraine. "Our neighbors' problems today are our problems tomorrow," said Kallas. title: Pemudik Sepeda Motor Terpantau Sudah Ramai Melintasi Kalimalang
description: KOMPAS.TV - Pemudik sepeda motor sudah terpantau ramai melintasi Kalimalang, Bekasi. meski hujan deras mengguyur pemudik tetap ramai berangkat ke kampung halaman.||||Di Jalan Kyai Haji Noer Ali, Kalimalang, Kota Bekasi, Jawa Barat pemudik sepeda motor dan warga yang pulang bekerja berjalan beriringan.||||Baca Juga Kominfo Luncurkan Buku Elektronik "Mudik Aman & Sehat" untuk Panduan Pemudik di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283399/kominfo-luncurkan-buku-elektronik-mudik-aman-sehat-untuk-panduan-pemudik||||Senin (25/04) malam, daerah Kalimalang sempat diguyur hujan deras, namun arus kendaraan terpantau tetap ramai.||||Diprediksi peningkatan pemudik sepeda motor akan terjadi pada 28 dan 29 April.||||Sementara, tujuh hari menjelang Idul Fitri Stasiun Pasar Senen terpantau ramai. Senen kemarin, sebanyak 15 ribu seratus penumpang diberangkatkan menggunakan 28 kereta api.||||Jawa Tengah dan Jawa Timur menjadi tujuan mayoritas dari para pemudik.||||Pembelian tiket untuk tanggal 27 April sampai 1 Mei 2022 mendatang sudah mencapai 98 persen.||||Calon pemudik yang belum membeli tiket disarankan memilih tanggal keberangkatan setelah tanggal 1 Mei.||||Arus kendaraan pemudik dari arah Jakarta di gerbang Tol Palimanan, Cirebon, Jawa Barat, Senin malam kian ramai.||||Selain mobil pribadi, bus dan travel mendominasi ruas Tol Palimanan.||||Tak ada kepadatan kendaraan di gerbang Tol Palimanan lantaran transaksi integrasi telah resmi diberlakukan sehingga pembayaran tol dilakukan di pintu keluar tol masing-masing.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283420/pemudik-sepeda-motor-terpantau-sudah-ramai-melintasi-kalimalang

title: How the James Webb Space Telescope Will Unfold the Universe | John C. Mather | TED
description: The James Webb Space Telescope is a miracle of modern science and engineering. With a 21-foot, gold-coated mirror protected by a sunshield that's the size of a tennis court, it's the world's most powerful telescope and humanity's latest attempt to answer questions like: "Where did we come from?" and "Are we alone?" (It also needed to be folded up like origami in order to launch into space.) Nobel Laureate John C. Mather, the leader of the team at NASA that built the Webb, explains how the telescope will observe the first galaxies to form in the early universe, peer behind clouds of cosmic dust and gas to reveal stars being born and uncover new details about places like Europa and Titan, which could harbor life. "We're going to get a great surprise from this telescope," Mather says.|If you love watching TED Talks like this one, become a TED Member to support our mission of spreading ideas: http://ted.com/membership|Follow TED! |Twitter: http://twitter.com/TEDTalks|Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ted|Facebook: http://facebook.com/TED|LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/ted-conferences|TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@tedtoks|The TED Talks channel features talks, performances and original series from the world's leading thinkers and doers. title: Meltdown in Pak after PM Modi's Jammu & Kashmir visit; Shehbaz Sharif tweets objection
description: A day after PM Narendra Modi visited Jammu and Kashmir, Pakistan has raised objections to his trip to the Union Territory. Pakistan PM Shehbaz Sharif in a tweet said that the PM's visit to Jammu was another bid to project 'false normalcy' in J&K. In particular, Sharif objected to the stone-laying foundation of various hydroelectric projects by the Prime Minister, calling it a violation of Indus Waters Treaty between India and Pakistan. title: Pelaku Minta Maaf! Akui Salah Mengira Nama Bobby Merupakan Nama Preman, Bukan Wali Kota Medan
description: MEDAN, KOMPAS.TV - Polisi resmi menetapkan RP, pria yang viral karena menolak membayar parkir elektronik dan mengancam juru parkir serta Wali Kota Medan, Bobby Nasution sebagai tersangka atas dugaan penganiayaan.||||Setelah ditangkap di Kabupaten Langkat, RP kini ditetapkan sebagai tersangka oleh polisi.||||RP dijerat dengan pasal penganiayaan, karena setelah mengancam juru parkir.||||Mobil yang ditumpanginya sempat menyebabkan sang juru parkir terseret, sehingga menyebabkan korban terluka.||||Korban terseret, setelah kaca mobil pelaku sengaja ditutup saat tangan korban masih menagih uang elektronik sebagai biaya parkir.||||Baca Juga Satgas Presisi Polrestabes Medan Berantas Geng Motor di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283289/satgas-presisi-polrestabes-medan-berantas-geng-motor||||Pelaku akhirnya ditangkap setelah korban melaporkan kasus ini ke polisi.||||Sementara itu, pelaku mengaku dirinya sempat pergi menjalankan mobilnya dan menutup kaca pintu mobol karena khawatir dengan tindakan juru parkir yang terkesan memaksa mengambil uang elektronik.||||Selain itu, dirinya sama sekali tidak berniat mengancam Wali Kota Medan, Bobby Nasution, karena mengira nama Bobby yang dimaksud juru parkir, adalah bos dari sang juru parkir yang disangkanya sebagai preman.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283396/pelaku-minta-maaf-akui-salah-mengira-nama-bobby-merupakan-nama-preman-bukan-wali-kota-medan

title: Johnny Depp Takes Stand For Cross-Examination In Week 3 Of Defamation Trial | LIVE
description: **Warning: This live stream will contain details some may find disturbing. Please watch at your own discretion.**|Johnny Depp takes the stand to be cross-examined during week 3 of his current defamation trial against ex-Amber Heard.|Depp sued Heard for $50 million following a December 2018 op-ed in the Washington Post in which she seemingly accused him of domestic abuse, despite not naming him. She has now countersued the actor for $100 million.|The trial is expected to take six weeks, with testimonies expected from James Franco, Paul Bettany and Elon Musk. title: Judge holds former President Trump in civil contempt
description: A New York judge is holding Donald Trump in civil contempt after the state's attorney general's office said he did not comply with a subpoena for documents as part of its investigation into the former President's company. title: White House Press Secretary on Elon Musk Purchasing Twitter

title: Dune: Spice Wars Early Access Review
description: Dune: Spice Wars Early Access reviewed by Leana Hafer on PC.||||Overall, I'm very impressed so far with Dune: Spice Wars. There are some balancing issues with the victory conditions and espionage mechanics, as well as the kind of minor bugs you'd expect from early access, but it's a layered, clever, generally well-balanced RTS with strong faction diversity, and it feels more or less finished even in its current early access state. The map looks great, and forces you to make interesting decisions about its deadly terrain and even deadlier inhabitants. Most remarkably, it manages to lay a lot of complex systems on the table while rarely feeling overstuffed or overwhelming. If this is just the launching pad for our adventures on Arrakis, I look forward to seeing where this one eventually lands, and I have no hesitation about recommending that strategy fans jump in now.|#IGN #Gaming #Dune
